A petition for review pursuant to Wis. Stat. 808.10 having been filed on behalf of the defendant-appellant-petitioner, Robert C. Stryker, pro se;

IT IS ORDERED that the motion to provide supplemental authorities is granted; and 
IT IS FURTHER ORDERED that the plaintiff-respondent, State of Wisconsin, is directed to serve and file a response to the petition for review on or before March 30, 2022.
